data.title: Office of the Registrar
data.meta_description: Find resources and answers to your questions about course schedules, transcripts, tuition payment, graduation and more.
data.text:
Welcome to the Office of the Registrar, where you will find resources and answers to your questions about course schedules, transcripts, tuition payment, graduation and more.

For help, select from the links or use the contact information provided below. Please note that to complete some interactive services such as online registration, you will be asked for your user name (student ID number) and password.
